data.description: Lovely 3 bed/2 bath, office, 2 car/garage, split bedroom floor plan in sought after Jupiter Narrows. Vaulted ceiling foyer and spacious great room, or living/dining area with a wall of sliding glass doors. Screened porch and landscaped fenced yard with mature trees. Outdoor oasis for relaxing/grilling. Oversized 2 car garage. 2023 Garage door.  2023 A/C Unit. Accordion hurricane shutters. Secluded neighborhood with beautiful tree-lined canopy entrance, 2 lakes and ocean breeze. Located in the heart of downtown Hobe Sound, walk/bike to shops and restaurants. Dog friendly beach is 1 mile away. Public boat-ramp with intracoastal access/ 2 miles away. Jupiter Narrows is the town favorite for Halloween.  Walk to the annual Hobe Sound Christmas Parade.  An amazing neighborhood with a low HOA.
